### 測試管理員訂單 API

### 1. 獲取管理員訂單列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer <管理員token>

### 2. 獲取管理員訂單列表（帶查詢參數）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/orders?page=1&limit=10&status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer <管理員token>

### 3. 搜尋訂單
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/orders?search=20250208
Authorization: Bearer <管理員token>

### 4. 獲取訂單詳情
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/orders/<訂單ID>
Authorization: Bearer <管理員token>

### 5. 更新訂單狀態為 CONFIRMED
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/orders/<訂單ID>
Authorization: Bearer <管理員token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED",
  "adminNote": "訂單已確認"
}

### 6. 更新訂單狀態為 SHIPPED
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/orders/<訂單ID>
Authorization: Bearer <管理員token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "SHIPPED",
  "adminNote": "訂單已出貨"
}

### 7. 更新訂單狀態為 COMPLETED
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/orders/<訂單ID>
Authorization: Bearer <管理員token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "adminNote": "訂單已完成"
}

### 8. 取消訂單
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/orders/<訂單ID>
Authorization: Bearer <管理員token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CANCELLED",
  "adminNote": "訂單已取消"
}

### 9. 刪除訂單（軟刪除）
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/admin/orders/<訂單ID>
Authorization: Bearer <管理員token>

### 10. 測試無效狀態變更（從 COMPLETED 到 PENDING）
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/orders/<已完成訂單ID>
Authorization: Bearer <管理員token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PENDING",
  "adminNote": "嘗試無效狀態變更"
}